text: Princess Estelle of Sweden, Duchess of Östergötland (Estelle Silvia Ewa Mary; born 23 February 2012) is the oldest child of Crown Princess Victoria of Sweden. Her younger brother is Prince Oscar, Duke of Skåne. She is second in line of succession to the Swedish throne. The princess was born at 04:26 Central European Time on 23 February 2012 at Karolinska University Hospital. She was named the following day. == Titles and styles and Honors == * 23 February 2012 – present: Her Royal Highness Princess Estelle of Sweden, The Duchess of Östergötland * Member of the Royal Order of the Seraphim (23 February 2012, presented 22 May 2012) * Member of the Royal Family Decoration of King Carl XVI (22 May 2012) * Recipient of the Commemorative Ruby Jubilee Medal of His Majesty The King (15 September 2013) * Recipient of the Commemorative 70th Birthday Medal of His Majesty The King (30 April 2016) * Recipient of the Commemorative Golden Jubilee Medal of His Majesty The King (15 September 2023) ==References== ==Other websites== *Royal Court of Sweden - Princess Estelle * |- Category:Swedish princesses Category:2012 births Category:Living people Category:People from Stockholm Category:House of Bernadotte Category:Royal Order of the Seraphim Category:Royal children
